description:
Danny recaps the first two episodes of Summer House, which featured a love triangle, a new cast member, Danielle?, and more! On Real Housewives of Atlanta, Kenya opens up to the other women and we ALMOST get to strippergate. Finally, Danny shares a few thoughts on part 1 of the RHOSLC reunion. There's also a Barb and Star caricature detour at the top of the show.


SUMMER HOUSE: 5:30ish

RHOA: 19:58ish

RHOSLC: 38:01ish
